snippet.title: She Dreams Elsewhere - Official Developer Video | Black Voices in Gaming 2024
snippet.description: Join developer Davionne Gooden at Studio Zevere for an introduction and update into She Dreams Elsewhere, an upcoming surreal adventure RPG where you must traverse an ethereal dreamscape, confront your inner nightmares, and escape from a never-ending coma. She Dreams Elsewhere will be available on PC, Xbox Game Pass, and Nintendo Switch.
